[[File:FijisiWood-TLC1.jpg|thumb|right|250px|Mara Jade rests against a pillar of Fijisi wood in the Imperial Palace]]
The '''Fijisi''' was a [[Species/Legends|species]] of [[Tree/Legends|tree]] native to the [[Planet/Legends|planets]] of [[Cardooine/Legends|Cardooine]] and [[Commenor/Legends|Commenor]]. The wood of this tree was used to create luxurious paneling and artwork. It had a delicate scent, even when polished.

At least one suite on the [[President's Guests floor]] in the [[Imperial Palace/Legends|Imperial Palace]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] was made of hand-carved Fijisi wood from Cardooine.

Fijisi wood was used for panels in some early [[RZ-1 A-wing interceptor/Legends|RZ-1 A-wing interceptors]], including the one [[Tycho Celchu/Legends|Tycho Celchu]] [[Pilot/Legends|piloted]] in the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]]. Celchu suspected that his craft was built on Cardooine.

